tntpsx Installer

tntpsx restores native TUN/TAP kernel extensions for Mac OS X Leopard 10.5.8 on PowerPC.

This installer provides:

- tap.kext
- tun.kext
- startup items for loading the kernel extensions at boot

Historical basis:
This recovery line is based on the historical tuntaposx 20090913-era code line.

Current recovery-line work includes:
- Leopard/PPC build restoration
- runtime verification
- installer roundtrip verification
- repository modernization
- documentation and cleanup

